citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:30 pm on
4/15/2025. The inspector attempted to contact the licensee/registrant by Phone calls to licensee's cell phone and home
phone. Knocked on the front door and garage door.. Failure to provide access to the facility, animals, and records for
inspection is a serious violation of the AWA and regulations. Failure to comply may result in enforcement action.
End Section
